What you need to know:

In all the league matches we played against them last season, they twice denied Bandari a chance to close the gap between them and bitter rivals Gor Mahia FCIn my honest opinion, the demotion due to match-fixing was not surprising because this is just the tip of the icebergI think that in as much as relegating Zoo sends a strong warning, it will not end match-fixing because match-fixers will get “wiser”